OL,3,CArrest made after suspicious death
OL,5,FAn arrest has been made as police
OL,6,Finvestigate a suspicious death in west
OL,7,FBelfast.
OL,9,FA police spokesperson said officers
OL,10,Fare at the scene of the incident in
OL,11,Fthe Helen's Wood Court area of
OL,12,FDunmurry.
OL,14,F"One person has been arrested and
OL,15,Fremains in police custody at this
OL,16,Ftime," they said.
OL,18,F"Enquiries are ongoing and an update
OL,19,Fwill be issued in due course."
